column2: SELECT  p.objID,p.ra,p.dec,p.type,p.skyVersion,p.run,p.rerun,p.camcol,p.field,p.obj,p.mode,p.flags, z.dr7objid,z.nvote,z.p_el,z.p_cw,z.p_acw,z.p_edge,z.p_dk,z.p_mg,z.p_cs,z.p_el_debiased,z.p_cs_debiased,z.spiral,z.elliptical,z.uncertain,  s.specObjID,s.sourceType,s.targetType,s.class,s.subClass, s.velDisp, s.z,s.waveMin,s.waveMax,s.elodieObject,s.elodieSpType,s.elodieBV,s.elodieTEff FROM   PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON s.specObjID = p.specObjID  JOIN zooSpec as z ON z.objid=p.objID and z.specobjid = p.specObjID where p.type=# and p.mode=# and p.objID=#
